                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-477-18480103 t18480103-477-punishment-64"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Maule.</hi>
